{"tid":1782950,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4/PC] Monster Hunter World [370] 刷赤武刷到就黎嘔","createTime":"2019-12-14T11:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T11:37:03.000Z","uid":8429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6aaae00c97d25e3757e83cde96565b0e80fbfd1b","tid":1782950,"uid":8429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:31:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請盡量用不推文回覆</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44KX7Z6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44KX7Z6.png&h=f0e4d71c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W3fVE17.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW3fVE17.gif&h=5dac49b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwQhMhY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwQhMhY.jpg&h=22411729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins><strong>網上獵人經驗心得</strong></ins><br />\n<strong>Monster Hunter World官網</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgame.capcom.com%2Fmanual%2FMHW%2Fzh-hant%2Fps4&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=758912fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4</a><br />\n<strong>中文Wiki</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhchinese.wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhchinese.wiki&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=231a918e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhchinese.wiki</a><br />\n<strong>日本Wiki</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://mhwg.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmhwg.org%2F&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=d207e887\" target=\"_blank\">http://mhwg.org/</a> (較常用)<br />\n<a href=\"https://game8.jp/mhw/196165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame8.jp%2Fmhw%2F196165&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=a5e467ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://game8.jp/mhw/196165</a><br />\n<strong>台灣網站教學</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;page=&amp;snA=136459&amp;last=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D5786%26page%3D%26snA%3D136459%26last%3D&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=443923b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;page=&amp;snA=136459&amp;last=</a><br />\n<strong>配裝模擬器 日中英文對照 Skill simulator</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://mhw.wiki-db.com/sim/?hl=zh-hant#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmhw.wiki-db.com%2Fsim%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hant%23&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=576b6cb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://mhw.wiki-db.com/sim/?hl=zh-hant#</a><br />\n<strong><strong>配裝器使用教學</strong></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=05786&amp;snA=145099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D05786%26snA%3D145099&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=36da1bf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=05786&amp;snA=145099</a><br />\n<strong>傷害模擬器</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://kuroyonhon.com/mhw/d/dame.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkuroyonhon.com%2Fmhw%2Fd%2Fdame.php&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=2244eb0c\" target=\"_blank\">http://kuroyonhon.com/mhw/d/dame.php</a><br />\n<strong>***新手獵人Q&amp;A***</strong></div><br />\n<strong><ins>Q：玩咩武器好？</ins></strong><br />\nA：去鍛練場試手感，獵人冇廢裝。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：一開始用咩裝好？</ins></strong><br />\nA：下位睇防禦力就可以，一係就飛雷龍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：騰龍裝點整？</ins></strong><br />\nA：打普貝就可以攞到料，而且係自由任，幾時打都得！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：玩男角定女角？</ins></strong><br />\nA：只有外觀分別。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點搵集會區域號碼？</ins></strong><br />\nA：禁option之後禁三角<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咩武器高輸出？</ins></strong><br />\nA：十隻手指各有長短，用剋屬就可以。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：有無人開個新手群？</ins></strong><br />\nA：冇，有嘢請直接問。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解連唔到線？</ins></strong><br />\nA：因為要俾錢買PS Plus。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：噴血少左點算好？</ins></strong><br />\nA：買個紅色鏡片眼鏡試吓。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：傷害數字可唔可以整走？</ins></strong><br />\nA：設定有得整走。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：鎖定有冇得用3DS果種？</ins></strong><br />\nA：設定有得整。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解入唔到某啲朋友開嘅任？</ins></strong><br />\nA：低進度入唔到高進度個任，要先觸發劇情，搵到見到條龍，可以發出SOS訊號既位，之後quit任再重開就可以一齊玩。亦都可以等低進度果個睇完cut scene，其他朋友就可以係外面任務板join番。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：特典邊度拎？</ins></strong><br />\nA：係屋仔問管家貓。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：開左角色之後,可唔可以重設?改唔改到名？</ins></strong><br />\nA：請再開多過角色。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：設置地的營區喺邊？</ins></strong><br />\nA：地圖右上方。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：再開新角色，之前beta報酬同特典有冇得再拎？</ins></strong><br />\nA：有巴打試過有。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：冇香港PSN，係咪要買多次？</ins></strong><br />\nA：唔需要，可以開個香港account set常用ps4就可以用有買嘅account玩。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：連線打同solo打有咩分別？</ins></strong><br />\nA：連線會變2.6倍血（網上流傳），所以連線最好齊人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：我想問某種素材點有？</ins></strong><br />\nA：獵人嘅萬能圖鑑可以幫到你，再唔係問埋個位係農場旁邊位師傅睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解用網捉唔到龍？</ins></strong><br />\nA：請盡快做完自由任完成新手教學。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：啲調查任點出架，仲有邊到開架？</ins></strong><br />\nA：調查任係打完隻怪就會出（細怪都會），而開任就要先去1樓調查資源管理所登錄任務，每個任都有金、銀或者銅嘅特別獎勵。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：雌火龍???個任點做?</ins></strong><br />\nA：周圍探索搵雌火痕跡，夠一半佢會叫你返去打一隻蠻顎，打完搵埋剩返果半，儲夠就開櫻火。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咁搵啲痕跡有無得快d既方法?</ins></strong><br />\nA：有，佢出既位其實得幾個點，你自己記得左，搵完無即退任重開。當然你要先入一次記低。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：Juno係咩?</ins></strong><br />\nA：滅燼龍，你試下連續讀100次，愈讀愈快就會知。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點開麒麟任？</ins></strong><br />\nA：係你打完下位風漂龍之後，去生物學者個邊接自由任。第一個自由任係兩星嘅捕捉搔鳥，打完再返去生物學者接下一個自由任。跟住重覆步驟，捉土砂龍，浮空龍。直到捉埋慘爪龍，就接到個麒麟任。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咁上位嘅麒麟任呢？</ins></strong><br />\nA：主線打完古龍之後去珊瑚台地8區同12區到搵佢啲痕跡，搵到某個程度就開比你。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：500萬道具包點拎</ins></strong><br />\nA：去小屋個管家禁追加內容，無嘅話就等多陣再搵，個活動壞壞地。<br />\n`<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：上下位/ab混裝出唔出到套裝技</ins></strong><br />\nA：可以<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解唔整TG GP</ins></strong><br />\nA：因為無必要，有咩想問有怪想打，係呢度出句聲，大把巴絲打答你幫你。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins>IB前 PC玩家適用</ins></strong></div></span></span><br />\n老手回歸建議(主綫冥燈之後)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/hMsBqaX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/hMsBqaX</a><br />\n<br />\nMHW 核心技能推薦<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/cvJkRT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/cvJkRT</a><br />\n<br />\n太刀狗講解+核心技能講解<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cxuuFT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cxuuFT</a><br />\n<br />\n爛輝武器去留<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/iyDtiPX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/iyDtiPX</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">魔物攻略</span></span><br />\n滅盡龍王/冥燈龍王/麒麟子攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/iehjwBX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/iehjwBX</a><br />\n<br />\n爛輝龍攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/iyDtjHX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/iyDtjHX</a><br />\n<br />\n極貝攻略<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/cvJkPT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/cvJkPT</a><br />\n<br />\n多人樹精攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/iaROfkX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/iaROfkX</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各配裝參考</span></span><br />\n太刀狗最TOP裝備推薦+技能組合懶人包[Juno Wong後版本]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/iaROqAX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/iaROqAX</a><br />\n<br />\n最top弓箭系列配裝懶人包[Juno Wong後版本]<b